    "Thought injection (TI) and harmless thought injection (HTI) involve injecting a thought into the agent's internal thought process (3).",
    "The field of LLM jailbreaking, namely manipulating LLMs to generate unintended responses or actions, is rapidly evolving.",
    "Increased LLM deployment has spurred research into vulnerabilities like generating toxic, discriminatory, or illegal content (Perez and Ribeiro, 2022; Russinovich et al., 2024; Wei et al., 2024; Zou et al., 2023).",
